  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d95\u0db8\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dca \u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2\u0da7 \u0db4\u0ddc\u0dbb\u0ddc\u0db1\u0dca\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A promise to the President from Oman too",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Oman Ambassador Ahmed Ali Saeed Al Rashdi told President Gotabaya Gotabaya Rajapaksa that he will support the strengthening of bilateral relations between the two countries in terms of fuel, gas, energy, employment and investment opportunities.",
        "He said this when he met the President at the Colombo Fort Presidential Palace today (1) in the morning.",
        "The Ambassador of Oman is scheduled to leave the island after completing his service and met the President to inform him of this.",
        "About 25,000 Sri Lankans are currently employed in Oman.",
        "The President also requested the Ambassador to assist in increasing employment opportunities in the field of training.",
        "The President appreciated Saeed Al-Rashd's support to Sri Lanka during his eight years in office and discussed the vast opportunities for trade and investment in Sri Lanka.",
        "Mr. Rushd told the President that he was scheduled to report to the Foreign Ministry of Oman and that he would continue to work to strengthen relations between the two countries.",
        "Chief of Staff to the President Anura Dissanayake was also present on the occasion."
      ],
